content.title: द्विघात समीकरण (Quadratic Equations) - भाग १ (Part 1)
content.description: The video begins with a general expression of a quadratic equations. Examples is given to emphasize the importance of quadratic equations in real life. Identification of whether an equation is quadratic or not is explained using examples. Roots of equations are then discussed. Method of factorization to get the roots is discussed. The example discussed earlier to explain the motivation for the quadratic equations is finally solved.
subject: Mathematics

content.title: द्विघात समीकरण (Quadratic Equations) - भाग २ (Part 2)
content.description: This video explains the method of finding the roots of a quadratic equation by completing squares. Later on, the formula method is introduced. The nature of roots are discussed at the end of the video with the notion of discriminant being introduced simultaneously. Illustrative examples are distributed throughout the video.
